        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="i8boH2LqC3hHRUDyFnox-71" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;glass=0;sketch=1;curveFitting=1;jiggle=2;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Auto-apply AI Agent ❗&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;1. Agent opens Dice portal in a sandboxed browser environment (playwright)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2. [HITL] Bench Sales Recruiter logs in with the candidates credentials&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3. Agent navigates to each Job posting and uploads the tailored Resume + Cover Letter&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;4. [HITL] Agent pauses for BSR to assist with any additional questions&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;5. Agent Submits the application.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
